Context: The user has an existing login to the system, has access to the database and application.

Primary Flow
	1. User navigates to the "Employee Management" section.
	2. User selects the "Create Employee" option.
	3. User enters new employee details 
	4. System validates the input fields.
	5. If validation succeeds, the system creates the employee record in the database.
System updates the employee list to reflect the new entry.

ALT FLOWS
	4a. If validation fails, the system displays an error message and prompts the user to correct the input.